  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package is issued at Model Risk Level 3 following an updated risk classification. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed and meet or exceed required levels. The 'Use error' factor is recorded as not-assessed on the grounds that operator interaction with the simulation tool is considered irrelevant to the COU; however, the correct encoding for that determination would be 'not-applicable', not 'not-assessed'. At MRL 3 this unassessed factor materially weakens the credibility argument.",
