      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA generic pump geometry",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements acquired at 2.5 L/min and 3500 RPM compared against CFD velocity predictions. Area-weighted RMS discrepancy of 4.2% observed across the impeller mid-plane. Validation activity judged sufficient for MRL 3 velocity QoI."
