      "rationale": "The assessment team concluded that use error does not apply to this COU because the CFD simulations are executed through a fully scripted, automated pipeline with no interactive operator input during runtime. Boundary conditions are set programmatically from a locked parameter file and results are post-processed by automated scripts. Consequently, no requiredLevel or achievedLevel has been established for this factor. Note: the appropriate factorStatus encoding for this determination is 'not-applicable'; the use of 'not-assessed' here is an encoding oversight that leaves the factor's credibility contribution unresolved at MRL 3."
