      "rationale": "Reynolds-averaged Navier-Stokes with SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on prior literature benchmarks for confined rotating flows at Re ~ 10^5. Non-Newtonian blood viscosity modeled via Carreau-Yasuda fit to donor data. Required level 2 met."
