    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed and meet or exceed required levels at MRL 3. The 'Use error' factor was judged by the assessment team to be inapplicable given the fully automated simulation pipeline; however, this determination was encoded as 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', leaving the factor formally unresolved. The review board accepted the package on the basis that the automated workflow mitigates practical use-error risk, while acknowledging that the encoding should be corrected in a subsequent revision to accurately reflect the not-applicable determination.",
